data.description: Welcome to this charming home with a great layout. It is just a few blocks from Willamette Falls Hospital and offers a light and airy floor plan with lots of potential for updating it your way! The owner is letting it go after 70 years of gardening and loving care. This 10,000 sf lot has a spacious 41' side yard, allowing room for a possible ADU, buyer to do their own due dilligence. The 2 car garage includes a separate room filled with shelving for storing canning jars, dark room, storage or? The improved 2nd level has plenty of additional attic space that could be converted to more living area. This home offers a unique opportunity for a new owner to put their finishing touches on it while enjoying a convenient location on bus line. There are not many homes currently for sale in the area with all of these amenities,  this one will go fast!
